name: Formula 5F6
details:
Foundation OverdriveThis is the Formula 5F6 from Catalinbread, a beautiful drive pedal designed to become the foundation of your entire rig with beautiful 50's tweed tones. This pedal has been set up to respond just like a real valve amplifier so you can chuck whatever you want into the front of this pedal to completely transform your tone.
